data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 3-bed, 2-bath gem! Modern updates throughout, featuring stainless steel appliances in the sleek kitchen. Enjoy the crisp elegance of new flooring on the main level. Prime location near the highway for easy city access, with top-notch restaurants and shopping just around the corner. Your dream home awaits! Schedule your showing today!
